des:
Welcome to Studio Moderna Home skill!
Now you can use voice to control multiple Smart products from Studio Moderna, like Robotic Vacuum cleaners, Purifiers, Bladeless Fan and many others.

After connecting Alexa to your products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our “Studio Moderna Home” app in app market then register an account;
(2). Configure our devices in our “Studio Moderna Home” app and change appropriate name for your devices;
(3). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market then configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(4). Search “Studio Moderna Home” skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(5). Enable “Studio Moderna Home” skill, and you'll be navigated to “Studio Moderna Home” login page;
(6). Follow the instructions on the page to complete linking;
(7). Now all setup is finished. You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:

“Alexa, turn on the vacuum.”
“Alexa, turn off the vacuum.”
“Alexa, turn on the air purifier.”
“Alexa, turn off the air purifier.”
“Alexa, turn on the fan.”
“Alexa, turn on the fan.”
